snippet.title: I've Transmigrated as the Supreme Villainess: Being an Annoying Roommate
snippet.description:
A parody game of Soul Union: https://coffeedripstudios.itch.io/soul-union
Where you play as some who is transmigrated into the role of the antagonist.

It's available at: https://coffeedripstudios.itch.io/itsv

Music: https://www.purple-planet.com

Thanks for watching and Happy Spring!
